{
  "texts": [
    "c During deployment, we use an inference method called Ensemble Refinement (ER).",
    "Here, the model stochastically generates multiple possible reports using a combination of temperature, top-p, and top-k sampling to capture different aspects of the input image.",
    "An aggregation module (GPT-4) then combines the results to provide a more complete description of the underlying case.",
    "Source data are provided as a Source Data file.",
    "these XATTN blocks are trained from scratch."
  ]
}